high_descs: Walk towards the island counter
Grab knife from the counter
Walk to the counter next to the fridge
Slice lettuce on the counter
Walk to the sink
Place knife in the sink
Walk towards the counter next to the fridge
Take a slice of lettuce from the counter
Walk towards the fridge
Put the slice of lettuce in the fridge and take it out
Walk towards the sink
Put the slice of lettuce in the sink
anns.task_desc: Slice the lettuce, put it in the fridge put it in the sink

high_descs: Walk forward and turn and face the end of the counter.
Take the knife from the counter.
Turn right, then left and approach the lettuce on the counter to the right.
Slice the lettuce on the right.
Turn left, then right and walk to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn around and walk toward the fridge then turn right and walk back to the lettuce on the left.
Take a slice of lettuce on the counter.
Turn left and walk to the fridge on the right.
Open the fridge, put the lettuce inside, and close the door. Then, wait a few seconds and remove the lettuce. Close the door.
Turn around and walk back to the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a refridgerated lettuce slice in the sink.

high_descs: Go forward to the wall, turn right, go forward a step, turn right to face the island counter.
Take the knife from the counter.
Turn right, go forward a step, turn left, go forward, turn right to the counter with the lettuce and the bread.
Cut the lettuce next to the bread into slices.
Turn left, go towards the door, turn left at the fridge, go forward to the counter to the left of the sink, turn right to face the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn right, go forward to the fridge, turn right, go forward, turn left to face the lettuce and the bread.
Take a slice of bread from the counter.
Turn left, go forward, turn right at the fridge, go to the fridge.
Chill the lettuce in the fridge, take the lettuce from the fridge.
Turn around, go forward to the counter to the right of the sink, turn right to face the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink to the right of the cup.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of cold lettuce in a sink.
